-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-12%2F68b7a910-15a7-11ea-bf27-46459b7bbbae&h=1d2d8143&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/25/Project_Power_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F25%2FProject_Power_Poster.jpg&h=ecf5c08b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d4/The_Invisible_Man_2020_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd4%2FThe_Invisible_Man_2020_poster.jpg&h=91d1f8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.《8級警戒》講述在科技進步的外來，擁有超能力卻不能帶來財富與機會，而是要躲藏警方即有意圖不法之徒，不只演員陣容大有來頭，以《環太平洋》《大亨小傳》幕後團隊打造震撼的視覺效果，是繼《成人世界》後又一科幻動作強片<br />\n<br />\n2.在紐奧良的街道上，關於一種神秘新藥的消息開始流傳開來，它能使每個服用者都持有超能力，包括能防彈的皮膚、隱形和超人般的力量。但這種藥丸卻讓城市的犯罪等級大幅提升，而使當地警察、一個十幾歲的商人和一名前士兵聯手、冒著高風險以追查並制止負責製造藥丸的組織<br />\n<br />\n3.無法忍受男友艾卓安長期的控制和虐待，西西莉亞在一個深夜偷偷給他下了安定藥，並在其熟睡之時起床收拾東西離開艾卓安的家。但在樓下車庫準備放走他們家的寵物狗宙斯時，宙斯撞到了車，觸發了警報。西西莉亞慌忙逃出，穿過森林，在公路上與其姐艾蜜莉會合，上了她的車。這時西西莉亞差點被趕到的艾卓安捉住，最終驚險逃脫。 <br />\n<br />\n11 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=e9cadd55\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=5ff3a7e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430ba6ae87caaeaa7b7aa34395e9caa49ec5cb92","tid":2158211,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T14:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3289ca3885a905eb7451f659d2fb1bfc53c7c1a8","tid":2158211,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c206e0216e5b93b39162c57b850be445f9fd1a","tid":2158211,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8182b0d9e9df4b6c50e278fa28eeaa10af92ad6d","tid":2158211,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T18:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}